mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;background:rgb(248,250,252);mso-shading:rgb(248,250,252);" >Department of Business Administration, University of Sahiwal</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
