color:rgb(34,34,34);font-weight:bold;font-size:12.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><br clear=all style='page-break-before:always'></span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:SimSun;color:rgb(30,41,59);
font-weight:bold;font-size:13.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face="SimSun" >1. Project Title</font></span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:SimSun;color:rgb(30,41,59);
font-weight:bold;font-size:13.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></b></h3><p class=p  style="mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-line-height-alt:12pt;" ><b><span class="15"  style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
font-weight:bold;" >University Examination Management System (ExamSys) with Role-Based Portals and Real-Time Analytics</span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';color:rgb(51,65,85);font-size:11.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><h3 style="mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-line-height-alt:12pt;" ><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:SimSun;color:rgb(30,41,59);
font-weight:bold;font-size:13.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face="SimSun" >2. Introduction</font></span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:SimSun;color:rgb(30,41,59);
font-weight:bold;font-size:13.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></b></h3><p class=p  style="mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-line-height-alt:12pt;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
color:rgb(51,65,85);font-size:11.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >In modern academic institutions, managing examination workflows, student course registrations, grading configurations, and academic transcripts is a highly critical yet complex administrative task. Traditional methods relying on paper sheets, manual calculation, and siloed spreadsheets are slow, labor-intensive, and prone to calculation errors.</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';color:rgb(51,65,85);font-size:11.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=p  style="mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-line-height-alt:12pt;" ><b><span class="15"  style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
font-weight:bold;" >ExamSys</span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
color:rgb(51,65,85);font-size:11.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&nbsp;is an automated, web-based examination control panel designed to streamline academic operations. The system implements secure, role-based access control (RBAC) isolating views and features for Administrators (Controller of Examinations), Faculty Members (Teachers), and Students. By utilizing automated grading calculations, real-time database-driven validations, and interactive visualizations, the system eliminates manual errors and speeds up results publication.</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';color:rgb(51,65,85);font-size:11.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><h3 style="mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-line-height-alt:12pt;" ><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:SimSun;color:rgb(30,41,59);
font-weight:bold;font-size:13.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><font face="SimSun" >3. Objective</font></span></b><b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:SimSun;color:rgb(30,41,59);
font-weight:bold;font-size:13.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></b></h3><p class=p  style="mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-line-height-alt:12pt;" ><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
color:rgb(51,65,85);font-size:11.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >To design and implement a secure, high-performance university examination database and portal system that:</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';color:rgb(51,65,85);font-size:11.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:4.5000pt;margin-left:36.0000pt;
mso-margin-top-alt:auto;text-indent:-18.0000pt;tab-stops:left blank 36.0000pt ;
mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-line-height-alt:12pt;mso-list:l6 level1 lfo1;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;color:rgb(51,65,85);
font-size:10.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >&#183;<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
color:rgb(51,65,85);font-size:11.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >Enforces secure </span><b><span class="15"  style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
color:rgb(51,65,85);font-weight:bold;font-size:11.0000pt;" >Role-Based Access Control</span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
color:rgb(51,65,85);font-size:11.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >&nbsp;(Admin, Teacher, Student).</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
mso-bidi-font-family:'Times New Roman';color:rgb(51,65,85);font-size:11.0000pt;
mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=MsoNormal  style="margin-top:5.0000pt;margin-bottom:4.5000pt;margin-left:36.0000pt;
mso-margin-top-alt:auto;text-indent:-18.0000pt;tab-stops:left blank 36.0000pt ;
mso-pagination:widow-orphan;mso-line-height-alt:12pt;mso-list:l6 level1 lfo1;" ><![if !supportLists]><span style="font-family:Symbol;mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;color:rgb(51,65,85);
font-size:10.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" ><span style='mso-list:Ignore;' >&#183;<span>&nbsp;</span></span></span><![endif]><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
