color:rgb(51,65,85);font-size:11.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;" >: A highly normalized MySQL database schema with 10 tables ensures data integrity, cascading updates, and constraints to prevent orphan entries (e.g., deleting a student cascades to clean up enrollments and marks).</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:Calibri;mso-fareast-font-family:SimSun;
